exadb-vm-cluster
****************


Description
===========

Details of the Exadata VM cluster on Exascale Infrastructure. Applies
to Exadata Database Service on Exascale Infrastructure only.


Available Commands
==================

* change-compartment

* change-exadb-vm-cluster-subscription

* create

* delete

* get

* get-update

* get-update-history

* list

* list-update-histories

* list-updates

* remove

* update
